name: Github
description: Github is a web-based hosting service for version control using Git. It is mostly used for computer code. It offers all of the distributed version control and source code management functionality of Git as well as adding its own features.

name: krakend
description: KrakenD is an ultra performant API Gateway with middlewares and plugins. It is designed for large companies, so it is scalable and easy to configure. It is a stateless, distributed, high-performance API Gateway that helps you to manage your microservices.

name: Microsoft
description: Microsoft Corporation is an American multinational technology company with headquarters in Redmond, Washington. It develops, manufactures, licenses, supports, and sells computer software, consumer electronics, personal computers, and related services.

name: Postman
description: Postman is a collaboration platform for API development. Postman's features simplify each step of building an API and streamline collaboration so you can create better APIsâ€”faster.

name: Zapier
description: Zapier is an online automation tool that connects your favorite apps, such as Gmail, Slack, Mailchimp, and over 1,500 more. You can connect two or more apps to automate repetitive tasks without coding or relying on developers to build the integration.
